author: juergen
msg: This is part of a major refactoring of the Search helper. Its goal is to be able to  process queries on computed WebDAV properties which are not stored in the NodeRevisionDescriptor.
In order to have a non-WebDAV-specific solution, a PropertyProvider may now be passed to the Search helper.
